quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  6,74,"[Janto] tuma nde Ibraa hiima maakannoo ben makko Aazara: \"Ea jogitoto sanamuuji reweteeЙ—i?\" Pellet, min miЙ—o yi'e an e yimЙ“e maa Й“en,e nder majjere Й“anngunde"
  6,75,"Ko wano non Men holliri Ibraahiima laamuuji kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, e fii yo o jeye e yananaaЙ“e Й“en"
  6,76,"Nde jemma on niЙ“Й“itunoo e makko, o tini hoodere, o maaki : \"Ndee Й—oo ko joomi am!\" ЖҒaawo nde mutii, o maaki : \"Mi yiЙ—aa mutooЙ“e Й“en"
  6,77,"Nde o tini lewru ndun no jalbi, o maaki : \"Nduu Й—oo ko joomi am!\" ЖҒaawo ndu mutii, o maaki : \"Si Joomi am fewnaali lam, ma mi jeye e yimЙ“e majjuЙ“e Й“en"
  6,78,"Nde o tinunoo naange ngen no jalbi, o maaki : \"Ngee Й—oo ko joomi am! Ko ngee Й—oo Й“uri mawnude\" ЖҒaawo nge mutii, o maaki : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, min ko mi daЙ—ndiiЙ—o e kon ko sirkoton"
  6,79,"Min dey mi fewtinirii yeeso am ngon e On TaguЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin ; ooГұiiЙ—o=haniifiyanke, min mi jeyaaka e sirkooЙ“e Й“en"
  6,80,"YimЙ“e makko Й“en wennji mo ; o maaki : \"E on wennjay lam fii Alla, gomЙ—ii le O fewnii lam? Mi hulataa kon ko kafidoton e Makko, si wanaa nde Joomi am Muuyi huunde. Joomi am yaajanii kala huunde anndal. E on waajitotaako"
  6,81,Ko honno mi hulirta kon ko kafiduЙ—on on hulaali onon le on kafidii Alla e huunde nde O Jippinanaali on hujja? Ko honnde e feddeeji Й—in Й—iЙ—i Й“uri hanndude e deeЖҙere? Si on laatike annduЙ“e
  6,82,"ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e jillaali gomЙ—inal maЙ“Й“e ngal e tooГұe, Й“en Й—on no woodani Й“e hoolaare, Й“en ko feewuЙ“e"
  6,83,"ЖҠun ko hujja Amen mo Men Okki Ibraahiima e dow yimЙ“e Makko Й“en. MeЙ—en ЖҒamtana darjaaji on mo Men Muuyi. Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a ko Г‘eeГұo, AnnduЙ—o"
  6,84,"Men Okki mo Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba Men fewni Й“e kala. E Nuuhu Men Fewni mo ko adii, hino jeyaa e jurriiyaaji makko, Daawuuda e Sulaymaana e Ayyuuba e Yuusufa e Muusaa e Haaruuna. Ko wano nii Men yoЙ“irta moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en"
  6,85,"E Zakariyaa e Yahyaa e Iisaa e Ilyaasa, kala maЙ“Й“e ko jeyaaЙ“e e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e"
  6,86,"E Ismaa'iila e Alyasa'a e Luutu, kala maЙ“Й“e Men ЖҒurnii e Winndere nden"
  6,87,"E baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en e Jurriiyaaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in e musiЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, Men SuЙ“ii Й“e, Men Fewni Й“e e laawol focciingol"
  6,88,"ЖҠum ko peewal Alla, himo Fewnira ngal on Mo O Muuyi e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. Sinno Й“e sirkuno, poЙ“ayno=yirbatna gaay e maЙ“Й“e kon ko Й“e gollaaynoo"
  6,89,"Ko Й“en woni Й“e Men Okki Deftere nden e Г‘eГұЖҙal ngal e Annabaaku ngun. Si Й“ee yeddii Й—in, gomЙ—ii Men Fawii Й—i yimЙ“e, Й“e laataaki yeddooЙ“e Й—i"
  6,90,"Ko Й“en woni Й“e Alla Fewni : ko peewal maЙ“Й“e ngal Гұemtintaa. Maaku : \"Mi lamndotaako e Й—um njoЙ“di\". Nde wonaali si wanaa waaju Winndere nden"
  6,91,"ЖҒe mawniniraali Alla no O haani mawninireede non tuma Й“e wi'unoo : \"Alla Jippinaali e neЙ—Й—anke hau e huunde\". Maaku : \"Ko hommno jippini Deftere nde Muusaa addi nden, ko nde annoora e peewal wonannde yimЙ“e Й“en? HiЙ—on waЙ—a nde Й—eri, feГұГұinon goЙ—Й—um e majji, suuЙ—on ko heewi.AnndinaЙ—on ko onon anndaano onon, wanaa baabiraaЙ“e mo'on. Maaku : \"Ko Alla\". Refti accaaЙ“e e jumpougol maЙ“Й“e hiЙ“e fija"
  6,92,"Ndee Й—oo ko Deftere nde Men Jippini : barkinaande, goonginnde ko woni yeesi mayre, e fii yo a waajor nde yimЙ“e Makko Й“en e Й“en wonЙ“e takko Й—on. ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e laakara, hino gomЙ—ini nden, kamЙ“e hiЙ“e reenoo e julde maЙ“Й“e nden"
  6,93,"Alaa Й“urЙ—o tooГұude haa foti wa on fefindiiЙ—o e Alla fenaande maa o wi'i : \"Wahayinaama e am\", hara hay huunde wahayinaaka e makko. E on wi'uЙ—o : \"Mi jippinay sugu kon ko Alla Jippini\". Sinno a tinuno nde tooГұooЙ“e Й“en woni e paЙ—Й—e maayde, hara Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en hino fonti juuЙ—e maЙ“e Й—en (no wi'a): \"Yaltinee pittaali mon Й—in. Hannde on yoЙ“ete lepte hoynooje sabu kon ko haalaynoЙ—on e hoore Alla ko wanaa goonga, laatiЙ—on gaay e Aayeeje Makko Й—en hiЙ—on mawnintinoo"
  6,94,"GomЙ—ii on ardirii Men telЙ—ugol, wano Men Tagirnoo on arannde laawol, on accii kon ko Men Jeynunoo on Й“aawo mon. Men Yiidaali e mon tefooЙ“e mon Й“en Й“e aaЖҙinoЙ—on wonnde kamЙ“e e mooЙ—on ko Й“e kafiduЙ“e. GomЙ—ii taЖҙondiral waЙ—ii hakkunde mo'on : majjirii on kon ko laatinoЙ—on hiЙ—on aaЖҙoo"